<p><a name="Highway_capable" id="Highway_capable"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Electric_car&amp;action=edit&amp;section=39" title="Edit section: Highway capable">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Highway capable</span></h3>
<dl>
<dt>Cars capable of at least 80 km/h</dt>
